_sText:
This City map has been made for css zombiemod long time ago by me and noobman and now i revamped it again and added more features.

Its designed for Normal Zombiemod and Zombie Hunt, specialised for "Teamplay", not recommended for Unlimited Ammo and permanent Noblock gameplay modes it ruins the balance.

**V4 Added/Fixed**

- 64 Players
- New Different Spawn Points
- Areaportals
- Tons of new Spots
- New Hatch door at cartunnel for entering passage (it can only open from inside)
- More enterable buildings
- Sewers
- Optimised spots
- Fixed Props
- Fixed Cubemaps
- Scary Zombie Illusions


Save hostages or trapped zombie !

You can play this map in our ZM server IP 85.131.171.119:27015

More info at [http://guncode.proboards.com/](http://guncode.proboards.com/ "Guncode Forum")
